	* src/iri.h: Fix #define for parse_charset
	* src/html-url.c: Surround some IRI code parts by #ifdef ENABLE_IRI
	* src/http.c: Likewise
	* src/iri.h: Likewise
	* src/recur.c: Likewise
	* src/retr.c: Likewise

