	* src/retr.c (fd_read_body): Be sure to measure timer when time has
	elapsed, too, not just when we've made progress.

2010-01-13  Micah Cowan  <micah@cowan.name>

	* src/openssl.c: Fixed some mixed declarations-and-code.

