2009-07-04  Steven Schweda  <sms@antinode.info>

	* vms/COLLECT_DEPS.COM, vms/config.h_vms, vms/decc_ver.c,
	vms/DESCRIP_CONFIG.MMS, vms/DESCRIP_DEPS.MMS,
