	* msdos/config.h: Removed unused defines, added needed 'HAVE_*' defines.

	* msdos/Makefile.DJ: rewritten to be used from './src' directory.
	Added '-DOPENSSL_NO_KRB5' for OpenSSL build. Target is
	now wget.exe.

