	* src/utils.c (base64_encode): Cast void pointer to char * before
	doing arithmetic.

2006-06-20  Hrvoje Niksic  <hniksic@xemacs.org>

	* src/utils.c (base64_encode): Made TBL const.
	(base64_decode): Made the base64_char_to_value table const.

