	* src/mswindows.c (inet_ntop): New function.  Print IPv6 addresses
	using WSAAddressToString.

2005-06-29  Hrvoje Niksic  <hniksic@xemacs.org>

	* src/wget.h: Remove obsolete definition of with_thousand_seps_sum.

