	(ALLOCA_ARRAY): Ditto.

	* src/html-parse.c: Renamed alloca_p to resized.
	(GROW_ARRAY): Renamed DO_REALLOC_FROM_ALLOCA to GROW_ARRAY and
	returned it to html-parse.c, since nothing else was using it.

