	* configure.in: Check for inline.

2001-04-11  Hrvoje Niksic  <hniksic@arsdigita.com>

	* src/url.c (parseurl): Don't strip trailing slash when u->dir is "/"
	because that strips the *leading* slash, thus forcing relative
	FTP retrieval.

