	* src/wget.h: added CONSSLERR
	* src/rbuf.c: ditto

	* src/http.c: Added HTTPS fuctionality.

	* src/retrc.c: Ditto.

	* src/url.c: Ditto.

	* src/init.c: Added opt.httpsproxy.

