	* src/utils.c (xmalloc): Renamed from nmalloc.
	(xrealloc): Renamed from nrealloc.
	(xstrdup): Renamed from nstrdup.

	* src/getopt.c (exchange): Use alloca.

	* src/mswindows.c (mycuserid): Use strncpy.

