	(http_loop): Likewise.
	(http_loop): Cosmetic changes.

	* src/connect.c (iread): Set errno to ETIMEDOUT in case of timeout.

	* src/retr.c (get_contents): Reset errno.

	* src/ftp.c (getftp): Minor fixes.

